it was important for people going to the ceremonies to show 
them there is opposition to these weapons she said 
pasadena is the first submarine and the third navy ship to bear 
the california citys name the 360foot submarine displaces 6900 
tons and will carry a crew of 12 officers and 115 enlisted men 
