shutters off the building protesters who broke into the building 
which had been closed smashed windows and started several small 
fires 
us officials had no immediate word on damage 
american dogs and god is great the protesters screamed 
as they hurled rocks at the building and drove away scores of police 
trying to guard it 
hang salman rushdie one protester yelled 
doctors at area hospitals who spoke on condition of anonymity 
