after a deadlock on organization day in late november 
negotiations finished on thanksgiving yielded a unique powersharing 
agreement 
it called for cospeakers one from each party presiding on 
alternate days cochairmen of the houses 28 committees and new 
rules designed to prevent one party from holding the other partys 
legislation hostage 
