<TEXT>
the prospect that ferdinand marcos may 
soon die presents his successor corazon aquino with the 
unpalatable decision of whether to let him return home 
it also has led to speculation about who will lead marcos 
followers upon his death 
the former president has been hospitalized in honolulu since jan 
