board which regulates savings and loans we turned it over to the 
department of justice as part of an ongoing criminal investigation 
sources who attended the meeting told the post that several 
issues were discussed including how to evade loan limits to one 
borrower and how to remove delinquent loans and foreclosed real 
estate from thrift books by selling them to other thrifts 
